				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="metadata topicon nopopups" id="protected-icon" style="display:none; right:55px;"><a href="Wikipedia_Protection_policy#move" title="This article is move-protected due to vandalism."><img alt="Page move-protected" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/58/Padlock-olive.svg/20px-Padlock-olive.svg.png" width="20" height="20" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/58/Padlock-olive.svg/30px-Padlock-olive.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/58/Padlock-olive.svg/40px-Padlock-olive.svg.png 2x" /></a></div>
